{"Id":224,"LanguageCodes":["rw","kin"],"Name":"kin-rmcrwanda","Author":"R. M. C. Rwanda","Language":"Kinyarwanda","Description":"Kinyarwanda","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://www.islamic-invitation.com/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nikinze kuri (Allah), Nyagasani w’abantu"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"Umwami w’abantu"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"Imana y’abantu"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"Ngo andinde ububi bwa (shitani) yoshya gukora ibibi, nyuma ikabireka (igihe umuntu yibutse Allah)"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"Yoshya imitima y’abantu gukora ibibi"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"Yaba (shitani) yo mu majini cyangwa mu bantu"}]}